sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Submit new channel name
    Frontend->>API: PATCH /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and owner permission
    API->>DB: Load workspace and channel
    DB-->>API: Workspace and channel found
    API->>DB: Update channel name
    DB-->>API: Channel updated
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + updated channel
    Frontend-->>Owner: Replace channel label in UI
